<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TutorLink Tutorial</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/app.css">
</head>

<body class="auth-page">

    <a class="brand auth-brand" href="/">
        <span class="brand-mark">T</span>TutorLink
    </a>

    <main class="auth-layout">

        <section class="auth-copy">
            <span class="eyebrow">Student Onboarding</span>

            <h1>Welcome to TutorLink!</h1>

            <p>
                Let's take a quick tour so you know where everything is before
                you start using TutorLink.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="form-card">

            <h2>Quick Tutorial</h2>

            <h3>1. Find Tutors</h3>

            <img src="/images/findTutors.png" alt="Find Tutors" class="tutorial-image">

            <p>
                Browse available tutors based on subject, date and time.
                Choose a suitable session and submit your booking request.
            </p>

            <hr>

            <h3>2. Navigation Bar</h3>

            <img src="/images/navbar.png" alt="Navigation Bar" class="tutorial-image">

            <p>
                Use the navigation bar to access your dashboard, available
                sessions, bookings, profile and logout anytime.
            </p>

            <hr>

            <h3>3. Dashboard</h3>

            <img src="/images/schedule.png" alt="Dashboard" class="tutorial-image">

            <p>
                Your dashboard keeps track of your upcoming tutoring sessions,
                booking requests and important updates.
            </p>

            <a class="button primary full" href="/tutorial/finish">
                Go to Dashboard
            </a>

        </section>

    </main>

</body>
</html>